on-Based Two-Factor Authentication and Localization Scheme for Autonomous Vehicles, Third International Workshop on Automotive and Autonomous Vehicle Security (part of NDSS), 2021.D. Callegaro and M. Levorato, Optimal Edge Computing for Infrastructure-Assisted UAV Systems, IEEE Transactions on Vehicular Technology, vol. 70, no. 2, pp. 1782 – 1792, 2021.A. Alsoliman, G. Rigoni, et al., COTS Drone Detection using Video Streaming Characteristics, in International Conference on Distributed Computing and Networking 2021, 2021, pp. 166 – 175.Y. Matsubara and M. Levorato, Neural Compression and Filtering for Edge-Assisted Real-Time Object Detection in Challenged Networks, in 2020 25th International Conference on Pattern Recognition (ICPR), pp. 2272 – 2279, 2021.
